Richard A. Ehst 
Executive Compensation
As President & COO at CUSTOMERS BANCORP INC, Richard A. Ehst  made $957,671 in total compensation.  Of this total $425,000 was received as a salary, $199,219 was received as a bonus, $276,018 was received in stock options, $49,228 was awarded as stock and $8,206 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


