Insider Activity


Individual




Richard A. Ehst



Mr. Richard A. Ehst is on the Board of Directors at Customers Bancorp, Inc., Albright College, Customers Bank (Phoenixville, Pennsylvania) and Pennsylvania Business Council. Mr. Ehst was previously employed as Regional President by Berks County Food Bank, EVP-Commercial Middle Market Division by Santander Bank NA, and President & Chief Operating Officer by New Century Bank (Phoenixville, Pennsylvania).



