President and COO of Customers Bancorp (NYSE:CUBI), Ehst Richard A, sells 2,970 shares worth $92,664
According to Customers Bancorp's most recent Form 4 filing with the SEC dated Mar 21 04:52 PM, company President and COO, Ehst Richard A disclosed selling 2,970 shares at a cost of $31.20. At the time of this transaction (Mar 21), this trade was worth $92,664 in total. As of Mar 21, Ehst Richard A now owns 118,793 shares in total worth about $3,661,200.26. 
For the last few recent trades made by Customers Bancorp (NYSE:CUBI) President and COO, Ehst Richard A, we have the following information:




SEC Form 4 filing: Mar 13: Sold 45,000 shares at the rate of $33.27 per share. Total worth of this trade was $1,497,150. Total number of shares owned as of Mar 13 were 67,438
SEC Form 4 filing: Mar 14: Sold 28,544 shares at the rate of $33.01 per share. Total worth of this trade was $942,237. Total number of shares owned as of Mar 14 were 67,438
SEC Form 4 filing: May 31: Sold 9,500 shares at the rate of $26.82 per share. Total worth of this trade was $254,790. Total number of shares owned as of May 31 were 93,467




